{"tid":1620630,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點解d人唔玩call/put輪，反而走去玩牛熊？","createTime":"2019-10-04T10:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T12:54:20.000Z","uid":123335,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"45f0ffaf771ea49704e7c5b8fa2285efdeb5a03c","tid":1620630,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:55:31.000Z","msg":"Eg 你睇個市係會升200點 <br />\n<br />\n點知佢先跌1000點，再倒升1200點 <br />\n最後真係升200點<br />\n你買call輪 or 做long call 就順利賺錢 <br />\n<br />\n但你買牛證呢<br />\n咁就伏鳩<br />\n跌1000點果陣，你已經死左<br />\n升返1200點果陣都唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛熊咁撚on9 <br />\n點解仲會有人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7d1b52373d0fc2de1579f59161e55045c63919","tid":1620630,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:55:57.000Z","msg":"難學"},{"pid":"2b369d8f268caac74305fffe861bc2a1e0203563","tid":1620630,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad7d1b52373d0fc2de1579f59161e55045c63919","tid":1620630,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:55:57.000Z","msg":"難學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:57:41.000Z","msg":"買幾次就識啦"},{"pid":"93c39355d4357b8b17253ff1cd1643a943f6ca4c","tid":1620630,"uid":40684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"有冇玩visa call"},{"pid":"c43c3e0dffdd250f9392d9820a357d411634c269","tid":1620630,"uid":207734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:23:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5acccd0cb567f32b2482bf1cefd212f3b370d8ed","tid":1620630,"uid":38540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:32:25.000Z","msg":"如果好似呢兩個禮拜橫行咁 輸時間值都輸死"},{"pid":"dd78ccbad24d04b49487f18d2c8c9b7dd0f70ee1","tid":1620630,"uid":303244,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:39:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7994757cab44648518c